<F P=100> National Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Suspends Electoral Commissions Activities </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Suspends Electoral Commissions Activities </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0206071694 Lvov VYSOKYY ZAMOK in Ukrainian 26 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> WS0206071694 </F>
<F P=104>  Lvov VYSOKYY ZAMOK </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Resolution by the Lvov Oblast Council of People's Deputies </F>
"On Suspending the Activities of the Commissions for Oblast 
Council Elections"] 
  [Text] Proceeding from the constitutional provision to the 
effect that the people are the superior and sole representatives 
of power; taking into account that as of today: 

  -  The provisions of Article 1 of the Law of Ukraine "On the 
Forming of Local Bodies of Power and Self-Government" have not 
been implemented; 
  -  Society's stance with regard to the state 
structure has not been determined, and normative acts about the 
structure and powers of the administration have not been 
adopted; 
  -  Unwilling to deceive the electors and thus plant 
disbelief and cause total degradation of the administration's 
prestige; 
  -  Realizing its responsibility for the fate of the 
state; 
  -  The Lvov Oblast Council of People's Deputies has resolved: 

  1. To suspend the activities of the territorial and 75 
district commissions for the elections of the chairman and 
deputies of the oblast council until a law is adopted on the 
structure and powers of the administration. 
  2. The resolution becomes valid on the day of adoption. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

