<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Signs Edict on Sale of State Enterprises </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Signs Edict on Sale of State Enterprises </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0206162194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1604 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0206162194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Moscow June 2 ITAR-TASS -- Russian President Boris 
Yeltsin has signed a decree ordering the sale of the state-owned 
enterprises unable to pay off their debts. 
  The decree is signed to promote the realization of the state 
policy aimed at preventing bankruptcy and negative social 
effects associated with the reorganization and liquidation of 
insolvent enterprises, should they be declared bankrupt. 
  The decree goes into effect from the moment of its 
publication. 

</TEXT>

