<F P=100> RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Military &amp; Nuclear Issues </F>
<H3> <TI>   Production of TU-160 Strategic Aircraft Discontinued </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Production of TU-160 Strategic Aircraft Discontinued </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0306083694 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 0730 GMT 3 Jun 
94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0306083694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow 2x2 Television </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Gorbunov aviation production association in 
Kazan has discontinued production of missile-carrying strategic 
TU-160 aircraft, the POSTFAKTUM-AERO agency reports. Each of 
these aircraft cost several billion rubles. A number of them 
manufactured recently have not yet been paid for by the army and 
are still at the enterprise's premises. 

</TEXT>

