<F P=100> Federal Assembly </F>
<H3> <TI>   Federation Council Approves Key Budget Figures </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Federation Council Approves Key Budget Figures </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0206131394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1130 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0206131394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Aleksandr Nechayev] </F>
  [Text] Moscow June 2 TASS -- The Federation Council, the 
upper chamber of the Russian parliament, approved at its 
closed-door meeting on Thursday the draft 1994 budget as the 
basis for further discussions which are to be held in its 
committees, TASS learned from the press service of the upper 
chamber. 
  If the discussion goes as scheduled, Chairman of the Budget 
Committee of the upper chamber Nikolay Gonchar will address the 
lower house on June 8 with the results of the work. No other 
details were disclosed. 

</TEXT>

