BFN 

  [Text] The Council of Ministers of Belarus has approved and 
submitted for confirmation to the Supreme Soviet a report on 
fulfillment of the republican budget for 1993. According to the 
report, the revenue was 2,106,904,000,000 rubles and the 
expenditure was 2,500,282,000,000 roubles. Therefore the 
expenditure exceeded revenue last year by 393,377,000,000 rubles. 

