<F P=106> [AZERTADZH report: "Agreement Signed"] </F>
  [Text] An agreement on the mutual handover of convicted 
persons between the Russian Federation and the Azerbaijan 
Republic has been signed in Russia's Justice Ministry. "It is 
intended to promote the interests of justice such that 
foreigners be afforded an opportunity to serve their sentence in 
the country of their citizenship," Yuriy Kalmykov and Ilyas 
Ismaylov, the ministers of justice of the two countries declared 
at a news conference held in this connection. 

</TEXT>

