<F P=103> LD0206181294 </F>
<F P=104>  Riga Radio Riga Network </F>
<F P=105>  Latvian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Daugavpils [town] council has presented a 
protest to the command of the Northwestern Group of Forces of 
the Russian Army concerning the fact that it is not observing 
the schedule agreed for the withdrawal of the army from the town 
and the provision of residences belonging to the special 
municipal services of the town, who cannot take over the 
unsupervised conditions and the ransacked apartments, depots, 
and storehouses. Restoration work is, in practice, carried out 
by workers paid by the municipal housing administration, but 
compensation for them has not reached the town, nor does it 
intend to place the burden of the expense on the people of 
Daugavpils. 

