<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Duma Budget Committee Sees No Way To Raise Spending </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MK0406083094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 4 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> MK0406083094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow SEGODNYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [SEGODNYA report: "Duma Budget Committee Against Upping </F>
State Spending"] 
  [Text] The State Duma Budget Committee does not think it 
possible to hike budget expenditures in line with 
recommendations passed by the senate. Committee Chairman 
Mikhail Zadornov thinks the budget calls for serious correction, 
but it should be accepted precisely in the shape submitted by 
the government. He pointed out that the main indicators of the 
level of expenditures, revenues, as well as the budget deficit 
were already approved in the first reading and cannot be 
changed, whereas an item-by-item redistribution of expenditures 
is not ruled out. 

</TEXT>

