<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Vesti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] The governing mayor of Berlin has refused to give 
permission for a brigade of Russian forces to take part in the 
joint farewell parade of the allied forces, which is to be held 
on 18 June. His says his decision is based on the USSR-FRG 
Treaty, according to which representatives of the Berlin 
garrison of the Western Group of Forces can visit West Berlin 
only privately. 

