  [Text] The Kyrgyz government delegation, led by President 
Akayev, has concluded its official visit to France. Key issues 
discussed in the talks were the prospects of economic and 
culture ties between Kyrgyzstan and France. The [words 
indistinct] visit in Paris, Akayev signed an agreement on 
