  [Text] Eduard Shevardnadze, the Georgian head of state, has 
said that President Boris Yeltsin has confirmed Russia's stance 
regarding the introduction and deployment of CIS peacekeeping 
forces in Abkhazia. According to the Georgian leader, Boris 
